BT 1 0 0 1 0 75 Tm /F1 9 Tf 12 TL -0.026118 Tw (We introduce a dimensionless parameter, the Wike-Ginzburg number W = T_operating / T_c, that quantifies the proximity of) Tj T* 0 Tw (any biological system to its coherence phase transition. For humans, W = 310 K / 330 K = 0.9394, placing the organism) Tj T* (squarely inside the Ginzburg critical regime where thermal fluctuations dominate mean-field behavior. We derive correlation) Tj T* (length enhancement xi ~ |1-W|^\(-0.63\) and susceptibility enhancement chi ~ |1-W|^\(-1.237\) from standard 3D Ising) Tj T* (universality class exponents. We compute W for 12 organisms spanning psychrophiles to thermophiles, propose a) Tj T* (W-Lifespan hypothesis, formalize fever and hypothermia as W-shifts, and connect W to the Wike Coherence Law gamma_c) Tj T* (= Omega/\(2*pi\). Eight testable predictions are provided.) Tj T* ET
